1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Eight Hundred=

2
00:01:57,210 --> 00:01:58,450
It's not that I'm lecturing you.

3
00:01:58,460 --> 00:01:59,900
(Year 1994)
Going to an illegal coal pit to treat people?

4
00:02:00,620 --> 00:02:01,740
And you got your leg mangled.

5
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:04,330
To put it nicely,
you accepted a buyout of your seniority.

6
00:02:04,330 --> 00:02:05,260
But to put it bluntly,

7
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:06,930
you were basically fired.

8
00:02:06,930 --> 00:02:08,170
And who did I do it for?

9
00:02:08,170 --> 00:02:09,450
Wasn't it for this family?

10
00:02:09,450 --> 00:02:11,410
Our expenses are so high now.

11
00:02:11,410 --> 00:02:13,500
Is your measly salary enough?

12
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:14,980
How many times have I said it?

13
00:02:14,980 --> 00:02:16,610
Don't worry about the money.

14
00:02:16,610 --> 00:02:18,340
I'll find a way eventually.

15
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:20,690
Songge's dialysis
costs 200 yuan per session.

16
00:02:20,690 --> 00:02:22,450
That's 1,600 yuan a month.

17
00:02:22,450 --> 00:02:23,540
With the salaries we had,

18
00:02:23,540 --> 00:02:24,450
could we even manage?

19
00:02:24,450 --> 00:02:26,290
So what? You bought out your seniority,

20
00:02:26,290 --> 00:02:28,410
and now, you're going
to look for a job like a youngster?

21
00:02:28,410 --> 00:02:29,380
But by taking the buyout,

22
00:02:29,380 --> 00:02:31,220
at least I got a lump sum.

23
00:02:31,220 --> 00:02:32,690
It can keep us stable for a while.

24
00:02:32,690 --> 00:02:34,060
What about when a kidney is found?

25
00:02:34,060 --> 00:02:35,290
The surgery costs 300,000.

26
00:02:35,290 --> 00:02:36,860
How will you solve that? Tell me!

27
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:38,320
Don't make things difficult for me.

28
00:02:39,210 --> 00:02:40,350
If I'm pushed to the limit...

29
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,720
If I'm pushed, I'll sell the house.

30
00:02:42,220 --> 00:02:43,570
Sell the house?

31
00:02:43,570 --> 00:02:45,060
What right do you have to sell it?

32
00:02:45,060 --> 00:02:46,260
Is this house even yours?

33
00:02:46,260 --> 00:02:48,380
It was a reward for Dad
saving someone back then.

34
00:02:48,380 --> 00:02:49,730
Besides, if you sell the house,

35
00:02:49,730 --> 00:02:51,110
will the five of us live on the streets?

36
00:02:56,450 --> 00:02:57,290
Songge,

37
00:02:57,850 --> 00:02:58,940
I'm going to leave here

38
00:02:58,940 --> 00:02:59,780
to earn money.

39
00:03:00,380 --> 00:03:02,060
I'll see if I can bring back even more.

40
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:04,230
That way, I can get you cured.

41
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,890
Just be patient for a while longer.

42
00:03:07,570 --> 00:03:08,780
Everything will get better.

43
00:03:10,380 --> 00:03:11,570
Chen Hui, I'm sorry.

44
00:03:12,690 --> 00:03:13,530
Why are you crying?

45
00:03:14,340 --> 00:03:15,180
Songge,

46
00:03:15,570 --> 00:03:16,820
never say "sorry" again.

47
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:18,820
This isn't your fault.

48
00:03:20,290 --> 00:03:21,660
No one wants to get sick.

49
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:23,940
Trust me.

50
00:03:25,170 --> 00:03:26,410
I will get you cured.

51
00:03:36,570 --> 00:03:37,410
Songge,

52
00:03:37,890 --> 00:03:38,890
before I come back,

53
00:03:39,890 --> 00:03:41,380
you must take good care of yourself.

54
00:04:01,690 --> 00:04:03,220
It's so late. Where did you go?

55
00:04:03,220 --> 00:04:04,170
And with Songge?

56
00:04:04,170 --> 00:04:05,730
Why are you being so nosy?

57
00:04:05,730 --> 00:04:06,660
What do you mean by "nosy"?

58
00:04:06,660 --> 00:04:08,060
So am I not allowed to have a say?

59
00:04:08,060 --> 00:04:09,220
It's their own business.

60
00:04:09,220 --> 00:04:10,690
- Why do you have so much to say?
- Go up and rest.

61
00:04:10,690 --> 00:04:12,380
What do you mean by "his own business"?
Is he not my son?

62
00:04:12,380 --> 00:04:14,060
Even if he's your son,
he has his own thoughts.

63
00:04:14,060 --> 00:04:15,410
Is it right to come back this late?

64
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:17,140
Why can't I say anything?

65
00:04:17,660 --> 00:04:18,580
Stop fighting, you two.

66
00:04:22,810 --> 00:04:24,290
Dad, Mom,

67
00:04:24,410 --> 00:04:25,250
I've made up my mind.

68
00:04:26,170 --> 00:04:27,210
I'm dropping out of school.

69
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:28,640
I'm going to Jin'gang to earn money.

70
00:04:28,930 --> 00:04:30,580
I'll take care of Songge's medical bills.

71
00:04:31,810 --> 00:04:32,650
What did you say?

72
00:04:33,140 --> 00:04:34,460
Let me tell you, Hui.

73
00:04:34,460 --> 00:04:35,660
Making money is for adults.

74
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:38,010
It's not something
you should be thinking about.

75
00:04:38,170 --> 00:04:39,220
Fengyang is only this big.

76
00:04:39,630 --> 00:04:40,480
So how do you two

77
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,810
plan to earn enough
for Songge's kidney transplant?

78
00:04:41,810 --> 00:04:42,810
I've already told you.

79
00:04:43,370 --> 00:04:44,250
This isn't something

80
00:04:44,250 --> 00:04:45,370
you should worry about!

81
00:04:46,290 --> 00:04:47,370
Right now, you just focus

82
00:04:47,370 --> 00:04:48,660
on repeating your final year

83
00:04:48,660 --> 00:04:49,850
and getting into university.

84
00:04:49,850 --> 00:04:51,460
Otherwise, I'll pull some strings

85
00:04:51,460 --> 00:04:52,810
to find you a job here in Fengyang.

86
00:04:52,810 --> 00:04:53,660
I don't want that.

87
00:04:53,660 --> 00:04:55,370
Does everything
have to go according to your plan?

88
00:04:55,370 --> 00:04:56,210
What's that?

89
00:04:56,370 --> 00:04:57,660
So you're all grown up now, huh?

90
00:04:57,660 --> 00:04:59,100
I'll handle my own business.

91
00:04:59,100 --> 00:05:00,700
I'm not cut out for studying anyway.

92
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:02,730
And I don't want
to stay in Fengyang anymore.

93
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:04,140
What's wrong with Fengyang?

94
00:05:04,140 --> 00:05:06,700
Tell me, what's wrong with Fengyang?

95
00:05:07,100 --> 00:05:08,730
Tell me. In Fengyang,

96
00:05:08,730 --> 00:05:10,170
you are my son.

97
00:05:10,170 --> 00:05:11,490
But what are you outside of Fengyang?

98
00:05:11,490 --> 00:05:12,980
You have no experience,

99
00:05:12,980 --> 00:05:14,290
and you have no certificates.

100
00:05:14,290 --> 00:05:15,810
You're nobody. Do you understand?

101
00:05:15,810 --> 00:05:17,220
Can you two please stop fighting?

102
00:05:17,220 --> 00:05:18,620
Just listen to what he's saying!

103
00:05:19,170 --> 00:05:20,850
Can you please just stop it?

104
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:25,100
You're right.

105
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:26,460
I'm a nobody.

106
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:27,850
I'm not here to negotiate with you.

107
00:05:27,850 --> 00:05:29,700
I've already made up my mind.

108
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:31,490
Anyway, I'm quitting school.

109
00:05:31,490 --> 00:05:33,440
I'll be responsible
for Songge's medical bills from now on.

110
00:05:34,980 --> 00:05:36,170
Hui.

111
00:05:36,170 --> 00:05:37,010
Hui!

112
00:05:39,060 --> 00:05:42,700
=Episode 13=
(Jin'gang)

113
00:06:16,050 --> 00:06:17,140
Why is this here?

114
00:06:25,980 --> 00:06:28,290
Dad, look at your son.

115
00:06:28,290 --> 00:06:30,490
He left such dirty clothes in Hui's room.

116
00:06:30,490 --> 00:06:32,220
Hui wore those back.

117
00:06:32,220 --> 00:06:33,700
How is that possible?

118
00:06:33,700 --> 00:06:34,540
Since when does Hui

119
00:06:34,540 --> 00:06:35,810
wear Hongbing's clothes?

120
00:06:35,810 --> 00:06:37,660
He was taken
to the police station by Hongbing.

121
00:06:37,660 --> 00:06:38,920
He wore this when he came back.

122
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:40,100
This was the outfit.

123
00:06:43,660 --> 00:06:44,500
What did you say?

124
00:06:45,170 --> 00:06:46,540
When was Hui

125
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:48,340
taken to the station by Hongbing?

126
00:06:48,340 --> 00:06:49,490
Last week,

127
00:06:49,490 --> 00:06:50,490
on your birthday.

128
00:06:51,050 --> 00:06:53,100
Hui called Songge.

129
00:06:53,730 --> 00:06:54,570
I overheard it.

130
00:06:55,490 --> 00:06:56,780
On my birthday?

131
00:06:57,930 --> 00:06:58,770
It

132
00:06:59,490 --> 00:07:00,660
was the day after we had cake.

133
00:07:03,610 --> 00:07:05,140
Hui even told me back then

134
00:07:05,140 --> 00:07:06,340
not to tell you.

135
00:07:06,340 --> 00:07:07,340
I just forgot.

136
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:11,700
(Computer Purchase List)

137
00:07:12,980 --> 00:07:13,930
Hui,

138
00:07:14,490 --> 00:07:15,490
you don't need to show me

139
00:07:15,490 --> 00:07:16,930
these accounts.

140
00:07:16,930 --> 00:07:18,100
Just let me know

141
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:19,340
the final cost.

142
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:20,980
Mr. Huang,

143
00:07:20,980 --> 00:07:22,610
we're partners.

144
00:07:22,610 --> 00:07:23,610
I have to tell you

145
00:07:23,610 --> 00:07:25,370
all the internet cafe's expenses.

146
00:07:25,370 --> 00:07:27,100
We're opening tomorrow.

147
00:07:27,100 --> 00:07:28,410
I even hired a lion dance

148
00:07:28,410 --> 00:07:29,540
to bring us good luck.

149
00:07:29,540 --> 00:07:30,810
A lion dance?

150
00:07:30,810 --> 00:07:32,490
That's great.

151
00:07:32,490 --> 00:07:34,020
Oh, Hui, after you go back,

152
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:34,930
stop by my house.

153
00:07:34,930 --> 00:07:36,220
Drive my Benz away.

154
00:07:36,220 --> 00:07:37,100
You can use it.

155
00:07:38,020 --> 00:07:38,860
I don't need it.

156
00:07:39,700 --> 00:07:40,780
If I leave it at home,

157
00:07:40,780 --> 00:07:41,780
no one can drive it.

158
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:43,410
It'll just rot
if it sits there too long.

159
00:07:44,050 --> 00:07:45,170
You're always in the city,

160
00:07:45,170 --> 00:07:46,050
so driving it

161
00:07:46,050 --> 00:07:47,250
will give you a good image.

162
00:07:47,250 --> 00:07:48,540
At the very least,

163
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:50,490
it's handy for hauling stuff.

164
00:07:51,460 --> 00:07:52,300
Mr. Huang,

165
00:07:52,490 --> 00:07:53,330
what's wrong?

166
00:07:53,810 --> 00:07:56,050
It's nothing. I caught a cold recently.

167
00:07:56,050 --> 00:07:56,930
I've been coughing.

168
00:07:57,660 --> 00:07:58,900
This won't do.

169
00:07:58,900 --> 00:07:59,900
You need to see a doctor.

170
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:01,980
It's fine.

171
00:08:01,980 --> 00:08:03,930
Just a respiratory infection.

172
00:08:03,930 --> 00:08:04,970
I'll be fine in a few days.

173
00:08:07,730 --> 00:08:08,580
How is your father?

174
00:08:10,610 --> 00:08:11,450
He

175
00:08:12,050 --> 00:08:12,890
is doing okay.

176
00:08:13,370 --> 00:08:14,490
My mom is there with him.

177
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:16,410
(Xiaojian Home Appliances)
Boss, I'll take this one.

178
00:08:16,410 --> 00:08:17,250
Alright.

179
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:18,490
Come pick it up in three days.

180
00:08:21,930 --> 00:08:22,770
Xiaojian.

181
00:08:23,460 --> 00:08:24,940
Mrs. Chen, buying appliances?

182
00:08:25,460 --> 00:08:26,980
No, I wanted to ask you something.

183
00:08:27,370 --> 00:08:28,340
What is it?

184
00:08:28,340 --> 00:08:29,180
Go ahead.

185
00:08:29,660 --> 00:08:30,900
Are you going to take over

186
00:08:30,900 --> 00:08:32,340
Hui's roller skating rink?

187
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:33,730
Who told you that?

188
00:08:33,730 --> 00:08:34,510
That business of his

189
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:36,340
is early mornings to late nights
and full of all kinds of rough people,

190
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:37,180
so I can't handle it.

191
00:08:39,850 --> 00:08:41,580
Well, a few days ago,

192
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:42,530
Hui

193
00:08:42,530 --> 00:08:43,460
came back to Fengyang.

194
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,300
Did you two have a drink together?

195
00:08:45,980 --> 00:08:47,250
No.

196
00:08:47,250 --> 00:08:49,770
It has been three or four months
since I last saw Hui.

197
00:08:50,580 --> 00:08:51,490
What's wrong?

198
00:08:51,490 --> 00:08:52,330
Is everything okay?

199
00:08:54,530 --> 00:08:55,370
It's nothing.

200
00:08:55,890 --> 00:08:56,730
I was just asking.

201
00:08:58,010 --> 00:08:59,370
I'll let you get back to work.

202
00:08:59,370 --> 00:09:00,210
I'm leaving now.

203
00:09:00,850 --> 00:09:01,690
Take care, Mrs. Chen.

204
00:09:05,130 --> 00:09:06,130
(Yingxiong)
Where should I put this?

205
00:09:06,130 --> 00:09:07,010
Just put it here.

206
00:09:07,010 --> 00:09:08,200
The firecrackers go here too.

207
00:09:08,530 --> 00:09:09,850
It's past mealtime.

208
00:09:09,850 --> 00:09:10,690
Are you hungry?

209
00:09:11,530 --> 00:09:13,220
We've been hungry for a while.

210
00:09:13,620 --> 00:09:14,940
If you're hungry, why didn't you say so?

211
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:15,980
I thought you could live

212
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:16,850
on air alone.

213
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:18,340
Get lost.

214
00:09:19,340 --> 00:09:20,890
I'll go buy some food for you.

215
00:09:20,890 --> 00:09:21,820
Keep tidying up.

216
00:09:21,820 --> 00:09:22,660
Okay.

217
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:26,780
Mrs. Chen.

218
00:09:28,940 --> 00:09:29,850
Liu Ning,

219
00:09:29,850 --> 00:09:30,770
let's go.

220
00:09:31,460 --> 00:09:33,370
How about we go buy the food instead?

221
00:09:33,370 --> 00:09:34,770
Alright, let's go.

222
00:09:34,770 --> 00:09:35,610
Let's go, Lei.

223
00:09:35,980 --> 00:09:37,530
- Hello, Mrs. Chen.
- Hello, Mrs. Chen.

224
00:09:39,940 --> 00:09:40,780
Mrs. Chen,

225
00:09:41,530 --> 00:09:42,420
anything?

226
00:09:46,340 --> 00:09:47,770
On the night of my birthday,

227
00:09:47,770 --> 00:09:49,130
Hui was caught by his dad

228
00:09:49,130 --> 00:09:51,100
and locked up for the night.

229
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:52,060
Did you know about this?

230
00:09:55,770 --> 00:09:56,610
Songge,

231
00:09:57,230 --> 00:09:58,810
you've never lied since you were little.

232
00:09:59,220 --> 00:10:00,420
You can't fool me.

233
00:10:00,420 --> 00:10:01,260
I know, Mrs. Chen.

234
00:10:06,530 --> 00:10:07,370
Why?

235
00:10:08,820 --> 00:10:10,420
It was just a misunderstanding that day.

236
00:10:11,130 --> 00:10:12,010
Mr. Chen released him

237
00:10:12,010 --> 00:10:13,250
the very next day.

238
00:10:13,850 --> 00:10:15,530
Chen Hui was just afraid you'd worry,

239
00:10:15,530 --> 00:10:16,980
so he didn't tell you.

240
00:10:17,340 --> 00:10:18,180
My husband

241
00:10:19,130 --> 00:10:21,130
has been a cop in Fengyang for 20 years.

242
00:10:21,770 --> 00:10:23,340
He's never suspected the wrong person,

243
00:10:23,340 --> 00:10:24,980
and he's never arrested
the wrong person.

244
00:10:25,650 --> 00:10:27,300
What did you and Hui do?

245
00:10:31,980 --> 00:10:32,820
Songge,

246
00:10:34,130 --> 00:10:35,850
I was being selfish before

247
00:10:36,420 --> 00:10:37,810
when I didn't want you two together.

248
00:10:38,650 --> 00:10:40,180
But Mr. Chen is different.

249
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:41,250
He's a policeman.

250
00:10:41,250 --> 00:10:43,340
He deals with serious matters of the law.

251
00:10:43,340 --> 00:10:44,980
You must tell me the truth.

252
00:10:45,530 --> 00:10:47,010
Mrs. Chen, it's really not like that.

253
00:10:48,250 --> 00:10:50,060
It really was just a misunderstanding.

254
00:11:02,220 --> 00:11:03,300
The more you say that,

255
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:06,250
the more unsettled I feel.

256
00:11:08,530 --> 00:11:09,940
I don't know if I should ask

257
00:11:11,300 --> 00:11:12,530
about this matter

258
00:11:13,490 --> 00:11:14,490
or if I should interfere.

259
00:11:16,180 --> 00:11:17,060
I don't know

260
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:20,060
if...

261
00:11:21,100 --> 00:11:22,250
If Hui

262
00:11:22,980 --> 00:11:24,100
really did something wrong,

263
00:11:25,940 --> 00:11:26,890
between the two of them,

264
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:30,340
whose side should I even take?

265
00:11:40,490 --> 00:11:41,730
Mrs. Chen, please don't cry.

266
00:11:45,220 --> 00:11:46,250
Don't be upset.

267
00:11:47,530 --> 00:11:49,610
Isn't Hui doing fine now?

268
00:11:50,340 --> 00:11:51,490
Besides, neither Hui nor I

269
00:11:52,130 --> 00:11:52,980
really knows

270
00:11:52,980 --> 00:11:54,060
the reason for it.

271
00:11:56,300 --> 00:11:57,140
Don't get stressed.

272
00:11:57,850 --> 00:11:59,420
Don't let it ruin your health.

273
00:12:09,010 --> 00:12:09,850
I hope...

274
00:12:13,220 --> 00:12:14,540
I hope what you're saying is true.

275
00:12:15,850 --> 00:12:16,700
I hope my husband

276
00:12:22,650 --> 00:12:24,220
has the wrong person this time.

277
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:30,090
Mrs. Chen.

278
00:12:34,770 --> 00:12:35,610
I know

279
00:12:37,100 --> 00:12:38,340
I owe your family.

280
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:42,460
I won't let Chen Hui

281
00:12:42,460 --> 00:12:43,610
come to any harm,

282
00:12:45,020 --> 00:12:46,100
even if it costs me my life.

283
00:12:53,490 --> 00:12:54,530
In this lifetime,

284
00:12:56,010 --> 00:12:57,180
I only have one wish.

285
00:12:59,300 --> 00:13:00,820
I just want this family

286
00:13:03,300 --> 00:13:04,700
to stay together.

287
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:36,060
Songge.

288
00:13:36,490 --> 00:13:37,530
You're back.

289
00:13:37,530 --> 00:13:39,370
Is everything ready for the opening?

290
00:13:39,370 --> 00:13:40,250
Yeah.

291
00:13:40,820 --> 00:13:42,460
I went to see Mr. Huang today

292
00:13:42,460 --> 00:13:44,250
and talked about the opening tomorrow.

293
00:13:46,460 --> 00:13:48,090
He's let us use his Benz.

294
00:13:50,610 --> 00:13:51,940
We have to work hard.

295
00:13:51,940 --> 00:13:53,130
We can't let Mr. Huang down.

296
00:13:53,130 --> 00:13:53,980
Definitely.

297
00:13:54,890 --> 00:13:55,820
I got you a gift.

298
00:13:57,650 --> 00:13:58,490
What do you think?

299
00:14:00,220 --> 00:14:01,940
Why are you buying me new clothes?

300
00:14:01,940 --> 00:14:03,460
You're the lady boss
of the internet cafe.

301
00:14:03,460 --> 00:14:05,580
Tomorrow is the opening,
so you have to look beautiful.

302
00:14:07,460 --> 00:14:08,300
Besides,

303
00:14:08,980 --> 00:14:10,650
this is a new beginning for us.

304
00:14:15,580 --> 00:14:16,420
Yes.

305
00:14:17,610 --> 00:14:18,820
Tomorrow is a new day.

306
00:14:20,610 --> 00:14:21,890
Everything will get better.

307
00:14:24,220 --> 00:14:25,460
It surely will.

308
00:14:32,130 --> 00:14:33,470
- You're back.
- Yeah.

309
00:14:33,490 --> 00:14:34,420
The food is cold.

310
00:14:34,420 --> 00:14:35,260
I'll go heat it up.

311
00:14:35,940 --> 00:14:36,780
No need.

312
00:14:37,100 --> 00:14:37,980
Forgot to tell you,

313
00:14:38,770 --> 00:14:40,300
I already ate at the station.

314
00:14:40,300 --> 00:14:41,150
That's fine.

315
00:14:41,160 --> 00:14:42,290
As long as you're not hungry.

316
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:48,660
What's making you so happy?

317
00:14:49,060 --> 00:14:49,900
Look at this.

318
00:14:51,250 --> 00:14:52,090
How is it?

319
00:14:52,420 --> 00:14:53,300
Does it look handsome?

320
00:14:53,890 --> 00:14:54,730
Show me.

321
00:14:58,370 --> 00:14:59,210
What do you mean?

322
00:15:00,460 --> 00:15:01,610
Isn't

323
00:15:01,610 --> 00:15:03,180
Hui's internet cafe opening tomorrow?

324
00:15:03,180 --> 00:15:04,250
If you're not busy,

325
00:15:04,250 --> 00:15:05,130
let's go take a look.

326
00:15:06,370 --> 00:15:08,010
What's so special about an opening?

327
00:15:08,010 --> 00:15:09,250
It's not like we haven't seen one.

328
00:15:09,250 --> 00:15:10,650
How can that be the same?

329
00:15:10,650 --> 00:15:12,300
That's our son's internet cafe.

330
00:15:12,300 --> 00:15:13,420
Besides,

331
00:15:13,420 --> 00:15:14,490
I want to go see it.

332
00:15:14,490 --> 00:15:16,410
I don't even know
what an internet cafe looks like.

333
00:15:19,790 --> 00:15:20,890
If you want to go, then go.

334
00:15:20,890 --> 00:15:22,460
I have things to do
at the station tomorrow.

335
00:15:22,460 --> 00:15:23,340
Get some rest.

336
00:15:33,130 --> 00:15:34,180
Not bad, Hui.

337
00:15:34,180 --> 00:15:35,580
You even brought in the Yue Lion Troupe.

338
00:15:35,580 --> 00:15:36,420
Just for good luck.

339
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:37,870
Internet cafes like this

340
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:39,730
are only just becoming
popular in first-tier cities.

341
00:15:39,730 --> 00:15:41,940
You're among the first group
of people to try this out.

342
00:15:41,940 --> 00:15:43,060
Try what out?

343
00:15:43,060 --> 00:15:44,250
I'm just happy to make a living.

344
00:15:44,250 --> 00:15:45,420
Look at you being humble.

345
00:15:46,890 --> 00:15:47,980
It's about time.

346
00:15:47,980 --> 00:15:49,100
Let's start the opening.

347
00:15:49,790 --> 00:15:50,730
Let's wait a bit longer.

348
00:15:54,770 --> 00:15:55,610
Mrs. Chen is here.

349
00:15:58,130 --> 00:15:58,970
Mom.

350
00:16:01,420 --> 00:16:02,940
- Hui.
- Where's Dad?

351
00:16:03,620 --> 00:16:05,620
Your dad has some
urgent business at the station.

352
00:16:06,730 --> 00:16:08,130
Come on, do the unveiling.

353
00:16:08,130 --> 00:16:09,530
No, I don't know how.

354
00:16:09,530 --> 00:16:10,580
- Come on, Mrs. Chen.
- No.

355
00:16:10,580 --> 00:16:11,420
Take a photo, Mom.

356
00:16:13,010 --> 00:16:13,850
It's so lively.

357
00:16:14,890 --> 00:16:16,460
The opening ceremony

358
00:16:16,460 --> 00:16:17,850
starts now.

359
00:16:17,850 --> 00:16:18,700
Three,

360
00:16:18,700 --> 00:16:19,560
two,

361
00:16:19,580 --> 00:16:20,420
one!

362
00:16:22,660 --> 00:16:23,820
(Yingxiong Internet Cafe)

363
00:16:23,820 --> 00:16:24,660
Happy opening!

364
00:16:30,540 --> 00:16:32,060
(Yingxiong Internet Cafe)

365
00:16:40,100 --> 00:16:40,940
It's so lively today.

366
00:16:40,940 --> 00:16:42,460
Why don't you say
a few words to everyone?

367
00:16:42,460 --> 00:16:46,790
A few words!

368
00:16:46,890 --> 00:16:47,890
Thank you, everyone.

369
00:16:47,890 --> 00:16:49,100
First, I want to thank

370
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,420
the friends who came to support us,

371
00:16:51,420 --> 00:16:53,250
and also my first wave of customers.

372
00:16:53,250 --> 00:16:54,890
Second, I want to thank my mom

373
00:16:54,890 --> 00:16:55,850
and Songge.

374
00:16:55,850 --> 00:16:57,130
Thank you for your support.

375
00:16:57,850 --> 00:16:58,940
Long story short,

376
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:00,220
third,

377
00:17:00,220 --> 00:17:02,010
we have a grand opening promotion today.

378
00:17:02,010 --> 00:17:03,130
However much you top up,

379
00:17:03,130 --> 00:17:04,770
we'll match it for free.

380
00:17:07,010 --> 00:17:07,850
Please.

381
00:17:09,620 --> 00:17:11,860
(Yingxiong Internet Cafe)

382
00:17:14,290 --> 00:17:15,660
We double your top-up amount.

383
00:17:16,490 --> 00:17:17,460
Welcome.

384
00:17:17,460 --> 00:17:18,570
Please come on in.

385
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:50,140
(Year 1994, Jin'gang)
Stay sharp when you go into the private rooms.

386
00:17:50,140 --> 00:17:51,380
Have some situational awareness.

387
00:17:51,380 --> 00:17:52,730
(Jin'gang Karaoke Sales)
Those who come to Jin'gang to spend money

388
00:17:52,730 --> 00:17:54,010
are our gods.

389
00:17:54,010 --> 00:17:55,290
If you piss off the gods,

390
00:17:55,290 --> 00:17:56,460
there will be consequences.

391
00:17:56,460 --> 00:17:57,660
Come on, let's review

392
00:17:57,660 --> 00:18:00,620
the Jin'gang's welcome greeting. Begin.

393
00:18:00,620 --> 00:18:01,770
- Your needs,
- Your needs,

394
00:18:01,770 --> 00:18:03,140
- our mission.
- our mission.

395
00:18:03,140 --> 00:18:04,380
- Excellent service,
- Excellent service,

396
00:18:04,380 --> 00:18:06,090
- never stop.
- Good.

397
00:18:06,090 --> 00:18:07,220
You saw it just now.

398
00:18:07,490 --> 00:18:08,410
My roller skating rink

399
00:18:08,730 --> 00:18:09,570
has great business.

400
00:18:09,770 --> 00:18:11,220
At this time of day,

401
00:18:11,220 --> 00:18:12,060
it's even busier.

402
00:18:12,420 --> 00:18:13,380
If business is so good,

403
00:18:13,380 --> 00:18:14,380
why stop all of a sudden?

404
00:18:16,010 --> 00:18:18,330
I'm not from around here.

405
00:18:18,330 --> 00:18:19,660
I can't handle

406
00:18:19,660 --> 00:18:20,700
the local thugs.

407
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:21,660
It's different for you.

408
00:18:21,660 --> 00:18:22,940
You're locals.

409
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:24,250
You don't need to fear them.

410
00:18:25,010 --> 00:18:25,850
Have a seat.

411
00:18:27,530 --> 00:18:28,370
Sir.

412
00:18:28,490 --> 00:18:29,740
Hello, your drinks are ready.

413
00:18:35,180 --> 00:18:36,020
Young man,

414
00:18:36,570 --> 00:18:37,410
this is for you.

415
00:18:38,530 --> 00:18:39,370
Thank you.

416
00:18:51,290 --> 00:18:52,130
Don't move.

417
00:18:52,810 --> 00:18:54,140
Police. Stay still.

418
00:18:54,140 --> 00:18:54,980
What are you doing?

419
00:18:55,420 --> 00:18:56,980
What's going on? What are you doing?

420
00:18:56,980 --> 00:18:58,580
You're Tian Jinhai, right?

421
00:18:58,580 --> 00:18:59,420
Yes.

422
00:18:59,420 --> 00:19:00,420
You should know

423
00:19:00,420 --> 00:19:01,620
what bad things you've done.

424
00:19:01,620 --> 00:19:02,460
I didn't do anything.

425
00:19:02,770 --> 00:19:03,700
Don't remember?

426
00:19:03,700 --> 00:19:04,910
Come back to the station with us.

427
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:06,380
On what grounds are you arresting me?

428
00:19:06,900 --> 00:19:08,490
Let me remind you.

429
00:19:08,490 --> 00:19:11,180
No. 126 Fanyu Road
looks like an entertainment center,

430
00:19:11,730 --> 00:19:14,530
but you should know what goods
are actually being stored inside, right?

431
00:19:15,180 --> 00:19:16,020
Sirs,

432
00:19:16,380 --> 00:19:17,420
let's talk this out.

433
00:19:17,770 --> 00:19:18,610
Everything

434
00:19:19,010 --> 00:19:20,010
is negotiable.

435
00:19:20,010 --> 00:19:20,850
Negotiable?

436
00:19:21,620 --> 00:19:23,490
Well, we're a bit short
on cash right now.

437
00:19:23,490 --> 00:19:25,530
How much are you willing to pay
to settle this?

438
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:27,260
What are you doing?

439
00:19:27,940 --> 00:19:28,790
Police business.

440
00:19:28,790 --> 00:19:29,990
What's it to you?

441
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:31,220
I've already called the police.

442
00:19:31,730 --> 00:19:32,770
They'll be here any minute.

443
00:19:34,290 --> 00:19:35,130
Right here!

444
00:19:35,320 --> 00:19:36,220
I'm the one who called.

445
00:19:36,220 --> 00:19:37,460
Real police. Let's go.

446
00:19:42,250 --> 00:19:43,090
Hai,

447
00:19:43,770 --> 00:19:44,610
let me see.

448
00:19:46,800 --> 00:19:48,090
Wait, let me unlock them for you.

449
00:19:53,620 --> 00:19:54,660
Don't worry, Hai.

450
00:19:54,660 --> 00:19:55,530
They were fake cops.

451
00:19:57,620 --> 00:19:58,530
How do you know?

452
00:19:59,060 --> 00:19:59,900
Real cops

453
00:19:59,900 --> 00:20:01,490
use double-locking handcuffs.

454
00:20:01,490 --> 00:20:02,510
These are clearly knockoffs.

455
00:20:03,420 --> 00:20:04,860
Not bad, young man.

456
00:20:05,380 --> 00:20:06,220
Here.

457
00:20:07,570 --> 00:20:08,570
Take it. Here.

458
00:20:08,570 --> 00:20:09,410
Go on.

459
00:20:10,460 --> 00:20:11,300
Thanks, Hai.

460
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:13,020
Young man,

461
00:20:13,460 --> 00:20:14,300
what's your name?

462
00:20:14,810 --> 00:20:15,770
I'm Chen Hui.

463
00:20:16,140 --> 00:20:19,460
(Public Phone)

464
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:23,450
Hello, Chen Hui.

465
00:20:23,450 --> 00:20:25,090
(Jin'gang Telecommunications)
How have you been doing over there?

466
00:20:25,090 --> 00:20:26,050
I'm doing great.

467
00:20:26,050 --> 00:20:26,890
Don't worry.

468
00:20:27,460 --> 00:20:28,770
How are Mom and Dad?

469
00:20:28,770 --> 00:20:31,010
Mrs. Chen still cries
whenever you're mentioned.

470
00:20:32,140 --> 00:20:33,980
Mr. Chen is still a bit angry with you.

471
00:20:38,180 --> 00:20:39,020
I see.

472
00:20:39,460 --> 00:20:40,900
Are you doing okay?

473
00:20:42,010 --> 00:20:42,900
I'm all good.

474
00:20:44,090 --> 00:20:44,930
Chen Hui,

475
00:20:45,250 --> 00:20:46,330
if you have time,

476
00:20:46,330 --> 00:20:48,250
you should still call home.

477
00:20:48,250 --> 00:20:49,090
What happened?

478
00:20:49,940 --> 00:20:52,250
Your parents
had another fight a few days ago.

479
00:20:52,250 --> 00:20:53,490
A really nasty one.

480
00:20:53,490 --> 00:20:55,110
They said they're going
to sell the house.

481
00:20:55,530 --> 00:20:57,250
Tell them they don't have to sell.

482
00:20:57,250 --> 00:20:59,050
Money comes fast for me here.

483
00:20:59,050 --> 00:21:00,090
Right now,

484
00:21:00,090 --> 00:21:01,530
I've saved up another 3,000 yuan.

485
00:21:01,530 --> 00:21:02,710
I'll wire it to you guys in a bit.

486
00:21:04,180 --> 00:21:05,020
Give it to me.

487
00:21:05,900 --> 00:21:06,740
Give it here.

488
00:21:08,970 --> 00:21:09,820
Hello.

489
00:21:10,980 --> 00:21:11,820
Dad.

490
00:21:12,140 --> 00:21:13,620
Think you're all grown up now?

491
00:21:13,620 --> 00:21:15,220
Since the day you left,

492
00:21:15,220 --> 00:21:16,700
you haven't called home once.

493
00:21:17,420 --> 00:21:19,290
Have you ever thought
about how worried we are?

494
00:21:20,940 --> 00:21:22,380
I'm sorry, Dad.

495
00:21:22,380 --> 00:21:23,250
Tell me,

496
00:21:23,250 --> 00:21:24,140
do you have any money?

497
00:21:24,140 --> 00:21:25,190
Can you even afford to eat?

498
00:21:25,980 --> 00:21:26,820
You...

499
00:21:27,050 --> 00:21:29,730
Find some time to call your mom
and let her know you're safe.

500
00:21:30,490 --> 00:21:31,900
Since you left,

501
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:33,660
she hasn't had
a single good night's sleep,

502
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:34,500
you know?

503
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:35,980
You brat,

504
00:21:35,980 --> 00:21:36,860
so you're hiding here.

505
00:21:36,860 --> 00:21:38,730
- What are you doing?
- Hui!

506
00:21:38,730 --> 00:21:40,110
- I'll kill you!
- What's wrong, Mr. Chen?

507
00:21:40,230 --> 00:21:41,070
Hello?

508
00:21:41,290 --> 00:21:43,030
Hui, can you hear me?

509
00:21:43,730 --> 00:21:45,220
- Brat, being nosy, huh?
- Hui!

510
00:21:49,730 --> 00:21:50,730
Ruined my plans.

511
00:21:51,050 --> 00:21:52,050
Wait.

512
00:21:52,050 --> 00:21:52,890
The money.

513
00:21:54,380 --> 00:21:55,250
Don't take my money.

514
00:21:55,250 --> 00:21:56,410
This is my life-saving money.

515
00:21:58,380 --> 00:21:59,290
Brat,

516
00:21:59,290 --> 00:22:00,620
that's for sticking your nose in.

517
00:22:00,620 --> 00:22:01,860
Don't let me catch you

518
00:22:01,860 --> 00:22:03,490
on this street ever again!

519
00:22:03,490 --> 00:22:04,330
Let's go.

520
00:22:05,660 --> 00:22:06,500
(Jin'gang Karaoke)

521
00:22:06,500 --> 00:22:09,290
Take good care of Li and Hai. Alright.

522
00:22:10,620 --> 00:22:12,530
Hui, look what time it is.

523
00:22:12,530 --> 00:22:13,420
Why just getting here?

524
00:22:13,420 --> 00:22:14,330
I'm sorry.

525
00:22:14,720 --> 00:22:15,810
What happened to your face?

526
00:22:16,210 --> 00:22:17,170
I accidentally tripped.

527
00:22:17,350 --> 00:22:18,220
Looking like this,

528
00:22:18,220 --> 00:22:19,770
won't you scare the guests away?

529
00:22:20,290 --> 00:22:21,180
Hui!

530
00:22:21,820 --> 00:22:22,660
Hui!

531
00:22:22,660 --> 00:22:24,090
Any orders, Hai?

532
00:22:24,090 --> 00:22:25,610
Not you. Go get Hui.

533
00:22:26,330 --> 00:22:27,620
Hui, quick!

534
00:22:27,620 --> 00:22:28,460
Hurry up.

535
00:22:28,620 --> 00:22:29,660
Get over here.

536
00:22:29,660 --> 00:22:30,900
- Hai.
- Drink with me.

537
00:22:32,290 --> 00:22:34,490
Everyone here is a good friend of mine.

538
00:22:34,490 --> 00:22:35,460
Today, you're with me.

539
00:22:35,460 --> 00:22:36,400
Let's have a few drinks.

540
00:22:36,420 --> 00:22:37,940
Come on, quiet down.

541
00:22:37,940 --> 00:22:39,330
Quiet down, please.

542
00:22:39,330 --> 00:22:40,770
Let me give a grand introduction.

543
00:22:42,090 --> 00:22:43,570
This young man here

544
00:22:43,570 --> 00:22:45,220
is the one who saved me the other day.

545
00:22:45,220 --> 00:22:46,060
Applause, please!

546
00:22:50,660 --> 00:22:51,660
Good.

547
00:22:51,660 --> 00:22:52,500
Go have fun.

548
00:22:52,740 --> 00:22:53,980
Come here.

549
00:22:58,810 --> 00:22:59,650
Here.

550
00:23:00,220 --> 00:23:01,090
I don't smoke.

551
00:23:01,090 --> 00:23:01,930
You don't smoke?

552
00:23:02,250 --> 00:23:03,850
Fine. Come.

553
00:23:04,050 --> 00:23:04,890
Have a drink with me.

554
00:23:17,180 --> 00:23:18,250
That day, at a glance,

555
00:23:18,250 --> 00:23:20,030
you knew if the handcuffs
were real or fake.

556
00:23:20,700 --> 00:23:22,700
Were you a cop before?

557
00:23:23,940 --> 00:23:25,010
No.

558
00:23:25,010 --> 00:23:26,290
My dad is the local

559
00:23:27,120 --> 00:23:28,870
Deputy Director
of the town police station.

560
00:23:31,050 --> 00:23:32,620
Where is your hometown?

561
00:23:32,620 --> 00:23:33,730
Fengyang.

562
00:23:33,730 --> 00:23:34,900
It's a small mining town.

563
00:23:35,860 --> 00:23:37,900
But, Hai, you probably
haven't heard of it.

564
00:23:37,900 --> 00:23:38,810
It's a small place.

565
00:23:38,810 --> 00:23:40,770
A deputy director of a small place?

566
00:23:40,770 --> 00:23:42,420
He can do whatever he wants there,

567
00:23:42,420 --> 00:23:43,460
just like Lee Rock.

568
00:23:44,290 --> 00:23:45,250
He's not that powerful.

569
00:23:46,530 --> 00:23:48,290
They say those miners

570
00:23:48,290 --> 00:23:49,460
are all very rich.

571
00:23:50,370 --> 00:23:51,250
Your hometown

572
00:23:51,250 --> 00:23:52,180
must be very lively.

573
00:23:52,770 --> 00:23:54,050
It is.

574
00:23:54,050 --> 00:23:55,500
They all say it's

575
00:23:55,510 --> 00:23:57,220
a "Little Hong Kong, China"
in the valley.

576
00:23:57,220 --> 00:23:59,010
Little Hong Kong, China?

577
00:23:59,010 --> 00:24:00,250
So impressive?

578
00:24:00,250 --> 00:24:01,350
I really didn't expect that.

579
00:24:02,770 --> 00:24:05,250
So you came from
"Little Hong Kong, China" to Jin'gang

580
00:24:05,250 --> 00:24:06,980
to make money?

581
00:24:07,530 --> 00:24:08,370
Yes.

582
00:24:10,140 --> 00:24:11,050
My girlfriend

583
00:24:11,980 --> 00:24:12,900
has uremia.

584
00:24:13,810 --> 00:24:15,110
I need to pay for her treatment.

585
00:24:15,770 --> 00:24:17,180
Uremia?

586
00:24:17,180 --> 00:24:18,770
That costs a lot of money.

587
00:24:18,770 --> 00:24:19,610
Yes.

588
00:24:19,900 --> 00:24:21,180
Relying on this job of yours,

589
00:24:21,520 --> 00:24:22,460
you won't make enough.

590
00:24:23,180 --> 00:24:24,420
By the time you've earned it,

591
00:24:25,220 --> 00:24:27,530
I'm afraid your girlfriend
won't be able to wait that long.

592
00:24:29,010 --> 00:24:30,250
I have no other choice.

593
00:24:33,660 --> 00:24:35,570
There are plenty of ways to make money.

594
00:24:35,570 --> 00:24:36,700
I'll teach you slowly later

595
00:24:36,700 --> 00:24:38,460
how to make lots and lots of money.

596
00:24:39,530 --> 00:24:40,570
We can talk more later.

597
00:24:40,570 --> 00:24:41,410
Come,

598
00:24:42,420 --> 00:24:43,460
have another drink with me.

599
00:24:44,090 --> 00:24:44,930
Cheers.

600
00:24:51,180 --> 00:24:52,050
Hai,

601
00:24:52,050 --> 00:24:53,290
sing a song.

602
00:24:53,290 --> 00:24:54,490
What should I sing?

603
00:24:55,180 --> 00:24:57,180
Anything is fine.

604
00:24:58,460 --> 00:24:59,770
Hai is going to sing!

605
00:24:59,770 --> 00:25:00,610
Clap, please!

606
00:25:16,980 --> 00:25:18,050
(Peidun Cough Syrup)
Sing a song!

607
00:25:18,860 --> 00:25:21,380
♪You're always too soft-hearted♪

608
00:25:21,380 --> 00:25:23,860
♪Too soft-hearted♪

609
00:25:23,860 --> 00:25:27,180
♪Crying alone until dawn♪

610
00:26:23,730 --> 00:26:24,570
Hui,

611
00:26:25,250 --> 00:26:26,090
are you awake yet?

612
00:26:28,010 --> 00:26:28,850
Hai,

613
00:26:29,490 --> 00:26:30,380
why am I here?

614
00:26:31,490 --> 00:26:32,570
You got wasted.

615
00:26:33,530 --> 00:26:34,370
So?

616
00:26:35,010 --> 00:26:36,190
Did you have fun last night?

617
00:26:37,570 --> 00:26:38,410
Last night,

618
00:26:38,620 --> 00:26:39,900
what liquor were we drinking?

619
00:26:40,570 --> 00:26:41,410
It wasn't liquor.

620
00:26:42,420 --> 00:26:44,140
It was Peidun Cough Syrup.

621
00:26:45,570 --> 00:26:47,810
Drink a bit of it, and you'll feel like
you're floating.

622
00:26:49,770 --> 00:26:50,770
Is it a drug?

623
00:26:51,220 --> 00:26:52,700
It's not a drug.

624
00:26:52,700 --> 00:26:53,900
It's medicine.

625
00:26:53,900 --> 00:26:55,010
But

626
00:26:55,010 --> 00:26:57,330
drinking it does feel addictive.

627
00:26:57,940 --> 00:27:01,090
Hui, do you remember
what we talked about yesterday?

628
00:27:03,620 --> 00:27:04,460
Come.

629
00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:07,570
You asked me how to make money.

630
00:27:09,010 --> 00:27:10,090
Yes,

631
00:27:10,090 --> 00:27:10,930
I remember.

632
00:27:12,140 --> 00:27:13,330
I'm here to tell you

633
00:27:14,530 --> 00:27:15,530
to join me

634
00:27:15,530 --> 00:27:16,770
in the cough syrup business.

635
00:27:16,770 --> 00:27:17,860
I guarantee

636
00:27:17,860 --> 00:27:19,010
it will save your girlfriend.

637
00:27:20,330 --> 00:27:21,660
The coal miners

638
00:27:21,660 --> 00:27:22,660
have plenty of money.

639
00:27:22,660 --> 00:27:24,250
They spend all day underground.

640
00:27:24,250 --> 00:27:25,660
It's exhausting and dangerous.

641
00:27:25,660 --> 00:27:27,140
If you sell this to them,

642
00:27:27,140 --> 00:27:28,700
they will love it.

643
00:27:28,700 --> 00:27:31,530
Plus, your dad is the Deputy Director
of the police station.

644
00:27:31,530 --> 00:27:32,620
With him covering for you,

645
00:27:33,090 --> 00:27:34,250
nothing can stop us.

646
00:27:38,530 --> 00:27:39,370
Hai,

647
00:27:40,290 --> 00:27:41,980
I don't think I can do this.

648
00:27:43,730 --> 00:27:44,620
Hui,

649
00:27:44,620 --> 00:27:46,490
I think you're smart enough

650
00:27:46,490 --> 00:27:47,330
and have vision.

651
00:27:47,330 --> 00:27:48,530
That's why I'm willing to help you.

652
00:27:48,530 --> 00:27:49,810
It doesn't matter if you don't do it.

653
00:27:50,310 --> 00:27:51,710
You can just keep working odd jobs

654
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:52,610
and slowly make money.

655
00:27:53,010 --> 00:27:53,850
Yes,

656
00:27:53,900 --> 00:27:54,740
you can wait,

657
00:27:55,660 --> 00:27:59,770
but can your girlfriend's life wait?

658
00:28:06,120 --> 00:28:08,220
In her condition,
she needs a kidney transplant soon.

659
00:28:08,220 --> 00:28:10,490
Otherwise, the complications
will only get worse.

660
00:28:10,490 --> 00:28:11,370
In Fengyang,

661
00:28:11,370 --> 00:28:12,660
you're my son.

662
00:28:12,660 --> 00:28:14,090
But what are you
once you leave Fengyang?

663
00:28:14,090 --> 00:28:15,530
You have no experience,

664
00:28:15,530 --> 00:28:16,900
and you have no certificates.

665
00:28:16,900 --> 00:28:18,860
You're nothing, you know?

666
00:28:18,860 --> 00:28:21,050
Your parents
had another fight a few days ago.

667
00:28:21,050 --> 00:28:22,420
It was a nasty one.

668
00:28:22,420 --> 00:28:23,770
They said they're going
to sell the house.

669
00:28:23,770 --> 00:28:24,860
How much do you want to make?

670
00:28:24,860 --> 00:28:25,980
380,000 in two years.

671
00:28:27,430 --> 00:28:28,290
380,000?

672
00:28:28,290 --> 00:28:29,130
In two years?

673
00:28:29,460 --> 00:28:30,300
Too greedy.

674
00:28:32,090 --> 00:28:32,930
Hai.

675
00:28:37,180 --> 00:28:38,940
I'll do it.

676
00:28:45,380 --> 00:28:47,690
Can you give me the equipment
from the roller skating rink?

677
00:28:48,700 --> 00:28:50,420
What do you want the stuff for?

678
00:28:51,420 --> 00:28:52,710
If I go back to selling medicine,

679
00:28:53,290 --> 00:28:54,460
I'll need a cover.

680
00:28:56,660 --> 00:28:57,500
Smart.

681
00:29:07,330 --> 00:29:09,610
Hai, what are you doing here?

682
00:29:10,090 --> 00:29:10,930
Hui,

683
00:29:11,660 --> 00:29:12,570
my good partner.

684
00:29:13,900 --> 00:29:15,010
Why did you suddenly

685
00:29:15,010 --> 00:29:16,330
disappear for months?

686
00:29:16,330 --> 00:29:17,290
I had to come see you.

687
00:29:18,700 --> 00:29:20,290
Let's find a place nearby to chat.

688
00:29:22,180 --> 00:29:24,050
Yingxiong Internet Cafe.

689
00:29:26,700 --> 00:29:28,010
Business is booming.

690
00:29:28,010 --> 00:29:28,850
Not bad.

691
00:29:28,870 --> 00:29:30,050
It's a popular spot.

692
00:29:30,940 --> 00:29:33,090
The machines are brand new.

693
00:29:33,090 --> 00:29:34,220
Each one must be expensive.

694
00:29:35,460 --> 00:29:36,300
Hai,

695
00:29:36,670 --> 00:29:37,940
there are too many people here.

696
00:29:38,570 --> 00:29:39,810
Whatever it is,

697
00:29:39,810 --> 00:29:40,860
let's find a place to talk.

698
00:29:40,860 --> 00:29:41,940
I'll buy you dinner.

699
00:29:41,940 --> 00:29:43,140
That's not right.

700
00:29:43,720 --> 00:29:45,310
Aren't you going to invite me in to see?

701
00:29:47,900 --> 00:29:48,740
Hai.

702
00:29:49,860 --> 00:29:50,700
This one.

703
00:29:51,460 --> 00:29:52,300
Try this one.

704
00:29:53,860 --> 00:29:55,460
Hello, Miss.

705
00:29:57,490 --> 00:29:58,820
Chen Hui, is he your friend?

706
00:29:59,090 --> 00:30:00,780
Yes, my friend.

707
00:30:01,220 --> 00:30:02,780
- Hello.
- Hello.

708
00:30:03,460 --> 00:30:04,300
Hui,

709
00:30:04,980 --> 00:30:06,330
your girlfriend

710
00:30:06,330 --> 00:30:07,330
is quite pretty.

711
00:30:08,330 --> 00:30:09,290
Here, Miss.

712
00:30:09,290 --> 00:30:10,130
Happy opening.

713
00:30:11,090 --> 00:30:12,380
Top up 1,000 yuan for me.

714
00:30:15,140 --> 00:30:15,980
Here.

715
00:30:17,140 --> 00:30:17,980
Well, thanks.

716
00:30:17,980 --> 00:30:19,050
Welcome to visit us often.

717
00:30:19,050 --> 00:30:19,890
Sure.

718
00:30:20,420 --> 00:30:22,220
Songge, you take care of the customers.

719
00:30:22,220 --> 00:30:23,310
I'm going to talk with my friend.

720
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:24,220
Okay.

721
00:30:24,660 --> 00:30:25,500
Let's go.

722
00:30:25,980 --> 00:30:26,820
Bye-bye.

723
00:30:29,540 --> 00:30:31,980
(Ruijin Hotel)

724
00:30:31,980 --> 00:30:32,820
Hui,

725
00:30:33,220 --> 00:30:34,220
why are you so nervous?

726
00:30:35,570 --> 00:30:36,410
You know me.

727
00:30:37,090 --> 00:30:38,820
I am quite easy to talk to.

728
00:30:39,770 --> 00:30:40,730
Hai,

729
00:30:40,730 --> 00:30:41,570
it's like this.

730
00:30:42,250 --> 00:30:43,700
Some things happened here lately,

731
00:30:44,220 --> 00:30:45,720
so I didn't have time to contact you.

732
00:30:46,460 --> 00:30:48,900
I know, you're here for
the payment for goods, right?

733
00:30:49,730 --> 00:30:50,730
Not just the payment.

734
00:30:51,770 --> 00:30:52,620
The interest, too.

735
00:30:53,050 --> 00:30:53,890
Right.

736
00:30:54,490 --> 00:30:55,420
Look, today

737
00:30:55,420 --> 00:30:56,330
won't work.

738
00:30:56,330 --> 00:30:57,330
I just opened.

739
00:30:57,730 --> 00:30:58,570
How about this?

740
00:30:59,010 --> 00:30:59,940
Tomorrow at 2 PM,

741
00:31:00,700 --> 00:31:01,900
wait for me on Hongqi Road.

742
00:31:01,900 --> 00:31:02,840
I'll give you the money.

743
00:31:03,530 --> 00:31:04,730
Can I trust you?

744
00:31:05,220 --> 00:31:06,060
Hai,

745
00:31:06,900 --> 00:31:08,700
my shop is right here.

746
00:31:08,700 --> 00:31:09,540
I can't run away.

747
00:31:12,900 --> 00:31:13,740
Fine.

748
00:31:14,420 --> 00:31:15,260
See you tomorrow.

749
00:31:17,700 --> 00:31:18,540
Take care.

750
00:31:24,700 --> 00:31:26,380
(Pawn)

751
00:31:26,380 --> 00:31:27,700
(Hongxing Pawnshop)

752
00:31:27,700 --> 00:31:28,540
Mr. Chen,

753
00:31:29,460 --> 00:31:31,090
let's get this straight first.

754
00:31:31,090 --> 00:31:32,090
(IOU)

755
00:31:32,090 --> 00:31:32,930
Last time,

756
00:31:33,290 --> 00:31:35,220
I heard Huang Liang mention your dad.

757
00:31:35,640 --> 00:31:37,520
If you're short
a single cent on the due date,

758
00:31:37,530 --> 00:31:38,980
I'll go to the Fengyang Police Station

759
00:31:38,980 --> 00:31:39,940
and ask your dad for it.

760
00:31:39,940 --> 00:31:40,980
Don't worry, Mr. Jun.

761
00:31:41,430 --> 00:31:42,290
When the day comes,

762
00:31:42,290 --> 00:31:44,380
I will return everything,
principal plus interest, for sure.

763
00:31:44,380 --> 00:31:45,220
Two hundred thousand.

764
00:31:45,530 --> 00:31:46,380
In six months,

765
00:31:46,380 --> 00:31:47,570
pay back 240,000.

766
00:31:47,570 --> 00:31:48,730
No problem.

767
00:31:48,730 --> 00:31:49,770
But I need it in cash.

768
00:31:51,210 --> 00:31:52,220
Count the money for him.

769
00:32:01,020 --> 00:32:02,180
Here's the payment I owe you,

770
00:32:02,180 --> 00:32:03,220
principal plus interest.

771
00:32:03,530 --> 00:32:04,380
It's 200,000 in total.

772
00:32:05,520 --> 00:32:06,530
You're really something.

773
00:32:07,220 --> 00:32:08,460
Going to a loan shark

774
00:32:08,460 --> 00:32:09,330
to get cash.

775
00:32:09,330 --> 00:32:11,010
This way, no one can ever trace it.

776
00:32:12,180 --> 00:32:13,420
I wasn't wrong about you.

777
00:32:14,860 --> 00:32:16,370
Hai, let me take you back to the hotel.

778
00:32:17,380 --> 00:32:18,220
Whatever you say.

779
00:32:26,530 --> 00:32:29,090
Hai, I've paid back the money I owed.

780
00:32:29,810 --> 00:32:31,010
From now on, we're even.

781
00:32:31,010 --> 00:32:32,420
Shouldn't you head back to Jin'gang?

782
00:32:34,030 --> 00:32:35,170
What's that supposed to mean?

783
00:32:35,380 --> 00:32:36,940
It means we're done with each other.

784
00:32:39,250 --> 00:32:40,090
Hui,

785
00:32:40,420 --> 00:32:42,420
of all the downline dealers
I've developed,

786
00:32:42,420 --> 00:32:43,490
you're the only one

787
00:32:44,290 --> 00:32:45,860
who hasn't had any trouble for years.

788
00:32:45,860 --> 00:32:47,890
You think you can just quit
whenever you feel like it?

789
00:32:47,900 --> 00:32:48,920
I told you from the start,

790
00:32:49,270 --> 00:32:51,810
once I saved enough for my girlfriend's
medical bills, I'd quit.

791
00:32:52,380 --> 00:32:53,220
You agreed to it.

792
00:32:54,010 --> 00:32:54,860
Hui,

793
00:32:54,860 --> 00:32:58,180
this life isn't something
you can just walk away from cleanly.

794
00:32:59,700 --> 00:33:00,770
Well, I'm quitting anyway.

795
00:33:00,770 --> 00:33:02,030
What are you going to do about it?

796
00:33:05,380 --> 00:33:06,530
If you quit,

797
00:33:08,220 --> 00:33:09,730
I'll report you to the police.

798
00:33:10,220 --> 00:33:11,980
You have no choice.

799
00:33:11,980 --> 00:33:13,310
Your crimes are heavier than mine.

800
00:33:15,020 --> 00:33:16,670
Well, there's
nothing more to talk about.

801
00:33:17,620 --> 00:33:18,770
You just wait and see

802
00:33:18,770 --> 00:33:20,330
if I'm bluffing or not.

803
00:33:36,570 --> 00:33:37,620
Still using this old trick?

804
00:33:38,860 --> 00:33:39,860
You think

805
00:33:39,860 --> 00:33:41,460
I'd come to see you
without being prepared?

806
00:33:41,460 --> 00:33:42,420
(Jiangbin City Kaixuanmen Grand Hotel)
Look at this.

807
00:33:42,420 --> 00:33:43,620
The hotel front desk receipt.

808
00:33:44,180 --> 00:33:45,340
Receipt for a report letter.

809
00:33:45,620 --> 00:33:46,490
If I can't

810
00:33:46,490 --> 00:33:47,620
return to the hotel today,

811
00:33:47,620 --> 00:33:49,620
this letter will be
mailed out tomorrow morning.

812
00:34:05,540 --> 00:34:07,740
(Jiangbin City Kaixuanmen Hotel)

813
00:34:11,130 --> 00:34:11,970
Hui,

814
00:34:12,570 --> 00:34:15,010
do you want to come inside with me
and see if I was

815
00:34:15,460 --> 00:34:16,300
bluffing you?

816
00:34:26,610 --> 00:34:27,460
Hello, sir.

817
00:34:27,460 --> 00:34:28,300
Hello.

818
00:34:29,570 --> 00:34:31,570
I'm staying in room 306.

819
00:34:31,570 --> 00:34:33,780
I left a letter here yesterday.

820
00:34:33,780 --> 00:34:35,660
Could you check
if it has been sent out yet?

821
00:34:35,670 --> 00:34:37,100
Certainly, sir. Please wait a moment.

822
00:34:38,340 --> 00:34:39,210
I'm sorry, sir.

823
00:34:39,210 --> 00:34:41,530
You brought the mail in
too late yesterday.

824
00:34:41,530 --> 00:34:43,090
But the mailman will be here soon,

825
00:34:43,090 --> 00:34:44,380
and it will be sent out shortly.

826
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:45,560
That's fine.

827
00:34:45,980 --> 00:34:47,460
I'll just have my friend mail it.

828
00:34:47,460 --> 00:34:48,300
Alright.

829
00:34:48,530 --> 00:34:49,370
Thank you.

830
00:34:53,210 --> 00:34:54,700
Go back and take your time reading it.

831
00:35:12,420 --> 00:35:14,820
(Report Letter)

832
00:35:21,170 --> 00:35:22,340
- Hello.
- Hello.

833
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:23,210
May I know

834
00:35:23,210 --> 00:35:25,410
which organization
this number sequence corresponds to?

835
00:35:25,980 --> 00:35:27,010
This looks familiar.

836
00:35:27,010 --> 00:35:28,220
Hold on, let me check for you.

837
00:35:31,090 --> 00:35:31,930
What's the number?

838
00:35:32,170 --> 00:35:35,090
951127.

839
00:35:35,090 --> 00:35:36,420
9511...

840
00:35:36,420 --> 00:35:37,260
(Jiangbin City)

841
00:35:37,260 --> 00:35:38,710
Here it is. It's the Municipal PSB's.

842
00:35:39,780 --> 00:35:40,620
Yes.

843
00:35:41,690 --> 00:35:42,530
Okay.

844
00:35:42,970 --> 00:35:43,820
Thank you.

845
00:35:43,940 --> 00:35:44,810
You're welcome.

846
00:36:23,060 --> 00:36:25,860
(Report Letter: Yingxiong Internet Cafe's owner,
Chen Hui, sells Peidun Cough Syrup)

847
00:36:51,340 --> 00:36:57,460
♪I always thought
once we see the full picture♪

848
00:36:58,780 --> 00:37:04,580
♪We could understand
each other with empathy♪

849
00:37:06,180 --> 00:37:12,620
♪I always thought
the path we never took♪

850
00:37:13,340 --> 00:37:18,940
♪Must have had more beautiful scenery♪

851
00:37:20,910 --> 00:37:27,030
♪I always thought
once we see the full picture♪

852
00:37:28,350 --> 00:37:34,150
♪We could understand
each other with empathy♪

853
00:37:35,750 --> 00:37:42,190
♪I always thought
the path we never took♪

854
00:37:42,560 --> 00:37:48,510
♪Must have had more beautiful scenery♪

855
00:37:50,220 --> 00:37:53,580
♪Keep moving forward
and don't look back♪

856
00:37:53,940 --> 00:37:57,180
♪The shore is only reached
by the road ahead♪

857
00:37:57,580 --> 00:38:00,420
♪Too much debt has accumulated♪

858
00:38:01,050 --> 00:38:04,790
♪Lit night♪

859
00:38:05,130 --> 00:38:08,690
♪Unfortunately, the breeze in town♪

860
00:38:08,890 --> 00:38:12,410
♪Can no longer catch up to the children♪

861
00:38:12,410 --> 00:38:15,570
♪Times have changed♪

862
00:38:15,970 --> 00:38:18,370
♪Now, everything♪

863
00:38:19,050 --> 00:38:23,210
♪Is no longer what it used to be♪
